Name: Accounting_x0020_Document_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the type of accounting document such as 1099 or invoice

Name: Applies_x0020_To
Description: Indicates the Murphy group company associated with an item

Name: Bank
Description: Indicates the name of a bank or financial institution

Name: Business_x0020_Function
Description: Indicates a major business function within Murphy

Name: Collateral_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the type of financial collateral e.g. escrow or parent company guarantee

Name: Commodity
Description: Indicates the tradeable commodities that Murphy deals with

Name: Counterparty
Description: Indicates the name of the counterparty in a transaction - financial or otherwise

Name: Counterparty_x0020_Contract_x0020_Number
Description: Indicates the contract number of a transaction in the counterparty's systems

Name: Document_x0020_Number
Description: Indicates a freeform generic document number

Name: Effective_x0020_Date
Description: Indicates the effective date for an item activity or transaction

Name: Hedging_x0020_Document_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the type of a hedging instrument such as mark to market or portfolio reconciliation statement

Name: HR_x0020_Policy_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the various HR policy types such as immigration tax transfer and vacation

Name: HSE_x0020_MS_x0020_Element
Description: Indicates the 11 essential elements of the HSE Management System

Name: Inactive_x003F_
Description: Boolean value indicating whether an item or document is active

Name: Incident_x0020_Id
Description: A freeform and generic identifier for an incident

Name: Issue_x0020_Date
Description: Indicates an issue date

Name: Level
Description: Indicates a level for an item or document in HSE Management System

Name: MOC_x0020_Expiration_x0020_Date
Description: Indicates an expiration date for an item or document

Name: MOC_x0020_Location
Description: Indicates a Murphy asset - field or block

Name: MOCDepartment
Description: Indicates a Murphy department

Name: Month
Description: Indicates the numeric value of a calendar month

Name: Murphy_x0020_Contract_x0020_Number
Description: Indicates a contract number for a transaction within Murphy's systems

Name: Murphy_x0020_Entity
Description: Indicates a Murphy group company - abbreviated form

Name: Policy_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the type of insurance policy such as auto aviation liability or worker's comp

Name: Quarter
Description: Indicates a business quarter

Name: Report_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates an operational report type such as shutdown or surveillance

Name: Retention_x0020_Code
Description: Indicates the retention code associated with an item or document. Murphy's corporate records management function is the custodian for this and document disposition is driven through retention policies and schedules which are based on this code.

Name: Signed_x0020_Date
Description: Indicates an action date attribute for a document or an item

Name: Stage
Description: Indicates a stage attribute for an insurance policy such as application audit or marketing

Name: Swap_x0020_Contract_x0020_Subtype
Description: Indicates the specific sub attribute or a contract type financial swap document e.g. Oil or NGL is the sub type of a commodity type swap contract

Name: Swap_x0020_Contract_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the specific contract type of a financial swap transaction such as a commodity currency or interest rate swap

Name: Swap_x0020_Document_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the document type of a financial swap transaction such as a confirmation or a contract or a netting agreement

Name: Swap_x0020_Unique_x0020_Identifier
Description: A freeform and generic unique identifier for a financial SWAP document within Murphy's systems

Name: Tax_x0020_Document_x0020_Type
Description: Indicates the type of tax document such as W8 or W9

Name: Year
Description: Indicates a chronological year
